name: Peach blossom enhancement
description:
It's simple, just a Lora to generate more peach blossom (especially with characters).

It's not a great one (cuz It looks just like pink flowers), but definitely usable. Anyway, I trained with images of peach blossom.

现存的模型里面比较容易生成的是樱花

为了能让人物的背景有更多桃花（树/林）元素而制作的一个Lora （当然从视觉上可能差不了太多，反正我是用桃花训练的）

Illustration image1

Illustration image2

The illustration (only use tags: 1girl, outdoors, peachblossom) shows that the effect varies with different models (I personally think this is because of existed element of peach blossom in checkpoints are different), so you can toy with the weight to get better result.

x/y图里面用了不同的模型生成的结果可以看出你原本用的大模型里面“含桃量"多少会影响这个Lora，所以请根据你使用的模型调解参数大小。

if it breaks your image, adjust CFG.

如果古神，试着调整CFG

刚玩Lora不久，还在摸索中，赐教欢迎，请教估计不太行…
